[thinking] **Thinking about database instantiation**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I’m pondering whether the server database only instantiates once a Java object is inserted. It seems like the database initializes its serializer lazily when it comes to serialization. I've set a name to save, and it’s interesting because the SessionRemote gets dynamic settings and immediately instantiates the client. Then, when I insert using JAVA_OBJECT, I wonder if it uses the server serializer and how the parameter gets transferred in that process.
[thinking] 
